			"updated": 1780682154470,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "Sub-layer 2 - Logical Link\nControl (LLC):\nLLC layer handles error\ncontrol, and the flow of\nmultiple protocols at once\nto communicate from MAC\nto Network layer (IP).",
			"rawText": "Sub-layer 2 - Logical Link Control (LLC):\nLLC layer handles error control, and the flow of multiple protocols at once to communicate from MAC to Network layer (IP).",
