			"updated": 1780695245073,
			"link": null,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "SAME (/24 same network): ARP directly to destination and no router involved    |    DIFFERENT (192.168.1.x -> 10.0.0.x): Packet sent to default gateway\n(router), which strips/rewrites L2 frame at each hop",
			"rawText": "SAME (/24 same network): ARP directly to destination and no router involved    |    DIFFERENT (192.168.1.x -> 10.0.0.x): Packet sent to default gateway (router), which strips/rewrites L2 frame at each hop",
