			"locked": false,
			"text": "Access port: sends/receives\nuntagged frames (single VLAN)\nTrunk port: carries tagged frames\nfor multiple VLANs\nNative VLAN: untagged traffic on\na trunk\nInter-VLAN routing: requires Layer\n3 (router or L3 switch)",
			"rawText": "Access port: sends/receives untagged frames (single VLAN)\nTrunk port: carries tagged frames for multiple VLANs\nNative VLAN: untagged traffic on a trunk\nInter-VLAN routing: requires Layer 3 (router or L3 switch)",
