			"locked": false,
			"text": "Multiplexes protocols to/from L3\nEtherType field identifies protocol:\n  0x0800 = IPv4\n  0x86DD = IPv6\n  0x0806 = ARP\n  0x8100 = VLAN tag\nFlow control + error notification",
			"rawText": "Multiplexes protocols to/from L3\nEtherType field identifies protocol:\n  0x0800 = IPv4\n  0x86DD = IPv6\n  0x0806 = ARP\n  0x8100 = VLAN tag\nFlow control + error notification",
			"fontSize": 12.888704910447174,
