		},
		{
			"id": "LXARamfx",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1087.3959811813656,
			"y": -2149.0048950032296,
			"width": 247.7065887451172,
			"height": 197.06363504198802,
			"angle": 0,
			"strokeColor": "#1a1a1a",
			"backgroundColor": "transparent",
			"fillStyle": "solid",
			"strokeWidth": 2,
			"strokeStyle": "solid",
			"roughness": 0,
			"opacity": 100,
			"groupIds": [],
			"frameId": null,
			"index": "f0LYTLc",
			"roundness": null,
			"seed": 593303,
			"version": 238,
			"versionNonce": 2103105816,
			"isDeleted": false,
			"boundElements": [],
			"updated": 1780695776475,
			"link": null,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "The IP Protocol field tells the OS\nwhich L4 protocol to hand data to:\n\n  6  = TCP\n  17 = UDP\n  1  = ICMP (ping/traceroute)\n  89 = OSPF (routing protocol)\n  47 = GRE (tunneling)\n\nIP delivers the packet --\nTCP/UDP is in the payload.",
			"rawText": "The IP Protocol field tells the OS\nwhich L4 protocol to hand data to:\n\n  6  = TCP\n  17 = UDP\n  1  = ICMP (ping/traceroute)\n  89 = OSPF (routing protocol)\n  47 = GRE (tunneling)\n\nIP delivers the packet --\nTCP/UDP is in the payload.",
			"fontSize": 14.331900730326403,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "The IP Protocol field tells the OS\nwhich L4 protocol to hand data to:\n\n  6  = TCP\n  17 = UDP\n  1  = ICMP (ping/traceroute)\n  89 = OSPF (routing protocol)\n  47 = GRE (tunneling)\n\nIP delivers the packet --\nTCP/UDP is in the payload.",
			"autoResize": true,
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"hasTextLink": false
		},
