			"updated": 1780693999371,
			"link": null,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "BROADCAST  vs  UNICAST  vs  MULTICAST",
			"rawText": "BROADCAST  vs  UNICAST  vs  MULTICAST",
			"fontSize": 26,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "center",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "BROADCAST  vs  UNICAST  vs  MULTICAST",
			"autoResize": true,
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"hasTextLink": false
		},
		{
			"id": "hs0cwdWX",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -475,
			"y": -860,
			"width": 653.5994262695312,
			"height": 325,
			"angle": 0,
			"strokeColor": "#1a1a1a",
			"backgroundColor": "transparent",
			"fillStyle": "solid",
			"strokeWidth": 2,
			"strokeStyle": "solid",
			"roughness": 0,
			"opacity": 100,
			"groupIds": [],
			"frameId": null,
			"index": "f0LYTMM",
			"roundness": null,
			"seed": 3546545,
			"version": 101,
			"versionNonce": 1033259800,
			"isDeleted": false,
			"boundElements": [],
			"updated": 1780693999371,
			"link": null,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "UNICAST:    One sender  ->  One specific receiver\n  Dst IP: 192.168.1.20  |  Dst MAC: AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF\n  Switch: forwards to exact port  |  Router: routes to exact host\n\nBROADCAST:  One sender  ->  ALL devices on subnet\n  Dst IP: 192.168.1.255  |  Dst MAC: FF:FF:FF:FF:FF:FF\n  Switch: floods all ports  |  Router: DROPS (does not forward)\n  Examples: ARP requests, DHCP discover\n\nMULTICAST:  One sender  ->  Group of subscribed receivers\n  Dst IP: 224.0.0.x (Class D)  |  Dst MAC: 01:00:5E:xx:xx:xx\n  Switch: floods (unless IGMP snooping enabled)\n  Examples: OSPF routing (224.0.0.5), video streaming",
			"rawText": "UNICAST:    One sender  ->  One specific receiver\n  Dst IP: 192.168.1.20  |  Dst MAC: AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF\n  Switch: forwards to exact port  |  Router: routes to exact host\n\nBROADCAST:  One sender  ->  ALL devices on subnet\n  Dst IP: 192.168.1.255  |  Dst MAC: FF:FF:FF:FF:FF:FF\n  Switch: floods all ports  |  Router: DROPS (does not forward)\n  Examples: ARP requests, DHCP discover\n\nMULTICAST:  One sender  ->  Group of subscribed receivers\n  Dst IP: 224.0.0.x (Class D)  |  Dst MAC: 01:00:5E:xx:xx:xx\n  Switch: floods (unless IGMP snooping enabled)\n  Examples: OSPF routing (224.0.0.5), video streaming",
			"fontSize": 20,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "UNICAST:    One sender  ->  One specific receiver\n  Dst IP: 192.168.1.20  |  Dst MAC: AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF\n  Switch: forwards to exact port  |  Router: routes to exact host\n\nBROADCAST:  One sender  ->  ALL devices on subnet\n  Dst IP: 192.168.1.255  |  Dst MAC: FF:FF:FF:FF:FF:FF\n  Switch: floods all ports  |  Router: DROPS (does not forward)\n  Examples: ARP requests, DHCP discover\n\nMULTICAST:  One sender  ->  Group of subscribed receivers\n  Dst IP: 224.0.0.x (Class D)  |  Dst MAC: 01:00:5E:xx:xx:xx\n  Switch: floods (unless IGMP snooping enabled)\n  Examples: OSPF routing (224.0.0.5), video streaming",
			"autoResize": true,
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"hasTextLink": false
		},
