			"text": "Automatically assigns:  IP address | Subnet mask | Default gateway | DNS server\nDORA Process (uses UDP broadcast):\n  1  DISCOVER: Client broadcasts to 255.255.255.255 (no IP yet)\n  2  OFFER: Server unicasts/broadcasts available IP to client\n  3  REQUEST: Client broadcasts acceptance\n  4  ACK: Server confirms assignment\n\nDHCP relay: router forwards DHCP between subnets (different broadcast domain)",
			"rawText": "Automatically assigns:  IP address | Subnet mask | Default gateway | DNS server\nDORA Process (uses UDP broadcast):\n  1  DISCOVER: Client broadcasts to 255.255.255.255 (no IP yet)\n  2  OFFER: Server unicasts/broadcasts available IP to client\n  3  REQUEST: Client broadcasts acceptance\n  4  ACK: Server confirms assignment\n\nDHCP relay: router forwards DHCP between subnets (different broadcast domain)",
			"fontSize": 20,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "Automatically assigns:  IP address | Subnet mask | Default gateway | DNS server\nDORA Process (uses UDP broadcast):\n  1  DISCOVER: Client broadcasts to 255.255.255.255 (no IP yet)\n  2  OFFER: Server unicasts/broadcasts available IP to client\n  3  REQUEST: Client broadcasts acceptance\n  4  ACK: Server confirms assignment\n\nDHCP relay: router forwards DHCP between subnets (different broadcast domain)",
			"autoResize": true,
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"hasTextLink": false,
			"link": null
		},
