			"text": "ROUTING PROTOCOLS (how routers learn routes)",
			"rawText": "ROUTING PROTOCOLS (how routers learn routes)",
			"fontSize": 24,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "center",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "ROUTING PROTOCOLS (how routers learn routes)",
			"autoResize": true,
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"hasTextLink": false
		},
		{
			"id": "rs_rp_b",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 595,
			"y": -367.4938812459627,
			"width": 647.0469360351562,
			"height": 261.25,
			"angle": 0,
			"strokeColor": "#1a1a1a",
			"backgroundColor": "transparent",
			"fillStyle": "solid",
			"strokeWidth": 2,
			"strokeStyle": "solid",
			"roughness": 0,
			"opacity": 100,
			"groupIds": [],
			"frameId": null,
			"index": "f0LYTMY",
			"roundness": null,
			"seed": 9378995,
			"version": 289,
			"versionNonce": 412845336,
			"isDeleted": false,
			"boundElements": [],
			"updated": 1780696067626,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "STATIC ROUTES: Manually configured. No overhead, no auto-update.\n  Best for small networks or specific traffic paths.\n\nDYNAMIC ROUTING PROTOCOLS: routers share topology:\n\nIGP (Interior -- within one AS / organization):\n  RIP  -- Distance vector. Metric: hop count. Max 15 hops. Simple.\n  OSPF -- Link state. Metric: cost (bandwidth). Dijkstra SPF.\n         Uses multicast 224.0.0.5 / 224.0.0.6\n  EIGRP -- Cisco hybrid. Metric: bandwidth + delay.\n",
			"rawText": "STATIC ROUTES: Manually configured. No overhead, no auto-update.\n  Best for small networks or specific traffic paths.\n\nDYNAMIC ROUTING PROTOCOLS: routers share topology:\n\nIGP (Interior -- within one AS / organization):\n  RIP  -- Distance vector. Metric: hop count. Max 15 hops. Simple.\n  OSPF -- Link state. Metric: cost (bandwidth). Dijkstra SPF.\n         Uses multicast 224.0.0.5 / 224.0.0.6\n  EIGRP -- Cisco hybrid. Metric: bandwidth + delay.\n",
			"fontSize": 19,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "STATIC ROUTES: Manually configured. No overhead, no auto-update.\n  Best for small networks or specific traffic paths.\n\nDYNAMIC ROUTING PROTOCOLS: routers share topology:\n\nIGP (Interior -- within one AS / organization):\n  RIP  -- Distance vector. Metric: hop count. Max 15 hops. Simple.\n  OSPF -- Link state. Metric: cost (bandwidth). Dijkstra SPF.\n         Uses multicast 224.0.0.5 / 224.0.0.6\n  EIGRP -- Cisco hybrid. Metric: bandwidth + delay.\n",
			"autoResize": true,
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"hasTextLink": false,
			"link": null
		},
