			"link": null,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "Protocol: IP (IPv4 / IPv6)\nData unit: Packet\nAddresses: IP addresses (logical)\nDevices: Routers, L3 switches\nKey tasks:\n  - End-to-end addressing\n  - Path selection (routing)\n  - TTL management\n  - Packet fragmentation\n  - Inter-network delivery",
			"rawText": "Protocol: IP (IPv4 / IPv6)\nData unit: Packet\nAddresses: IP addresses (logical)\nDevices: Routers, L3 switches\nKey tasks:\n  - End-to-end addressing\n  - Path selection (routing)\n  - TTL management\n  - Packet fragmentation\n  - Inter-network delivery",
			"fontSize": 20,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "Protocol: IP (IPv4 / IPv6)\nData unit: Packet\nAddresses: IP addresses (logical)\nDevices: Routers, L3 switches\nKey tasks:\n  - End-to-end addressing\n  - Path selection (routing)\n  - TTL management\n  - Packet fragmentation\n  - Inter-network delivery",
			"autoResize": true,
