			"link": null,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "Protocol: Ethernet, Wi-Fi, PPP\nData unit: Frame\nAddresses: MAC addresses (hardware)\nDevices: Switches, bridges, NICs\nKey tasks:\n  - Framing (add/strip headers)\n  - MAC addressing\n  - Error detection (FCS/CRC)\n  - Access control (CSMA)\n  - VLAN segmentation",
			"rawText": "Protocol: Ethernet, Wi-Fi, PPP\nData unit: Frame\nAddresses: MAC addresses (hardware)\nDevices: Switches, bridges, NICs\nKey tasks:\n  - Framing (add/strip headers)\n  - MAC addressing\n  - Error detection (FCS/CRC)\n  - Access control (CSMA)\n  - VLAN segmentation",
			"fontSize": 20,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "Protocol: Ethernet, Wi-Fi, PPP\nData unit: Frame\nAddresses: MAC addresses (hardware)\nDevices: Switches, bridges, NICs\nKey tasks:\n  - Framing (add/strip headers)\n  - MAC addressing\n  - Error detection (FCS/CRC)\n  - Access control (CSMA)\n  - VLAN segmentation",
			"autoResize": true,
