			"locked": false,
			"text": "Protocol: IEEE 802.3, 802.11\nData unit: Bits (0s and 1s)\nAddresses: None\nDevices: Hubs, repeaters, NICs, cables\nKey tasks:\n  - Physical signal transmission\n  - Bit encoding/decoding\n  - Voltage/light/radio modulation\n  - Cable/connector standards\n  - Duplex negotiation",
			"rawText": "Protocol: IEEE 802.3, 802.11\nData unit: Bits (0s and 1s)\nAddresses: None\nDevices: Hubs, repeaters, NICs, cables\nKey tasks:\n  - Physical signal transmission\n  - Bit encoding/decoding\n  - Voltage/light/radio modulation\n  - Cable/connector standards\n  - Duplex negotiation",
