			"boundElements": [],
			"updated": 1780696093803,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "\nEGP (Exterior -- between organizations / ISPs):\n  BGP  -- Border Gateway Protocol. The internet routing protocol.\n         Path vector. Policy-based routing between ASes.\n\nAdmin Distance (preference when multiple routes exist):\n  Connected=0  Static=1  OSPF=110  RIP=120  BGP=200",
			"rawText": "\nEGP (Exterior -- between organizations / ISPs):\n  BGP  -- Border Gateway Protocol. The internet routing protocol.\n         Path vector. Policy-based routing between ASes.\n\nAdmin Distance (preference when multiple routes exist):\n  Connected=0  Static=1  OSPF=110  RIP=120  BGP=200",
			"fontSize": 15.717782145164174,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "\nEGP (Exterior -- between organizations / ISPs):\n  BGP  -- Border Gateway Protocol. The internet routing protocol.\n         Path vector. Policy-based routing between ASes.\n\nAdmin Distance (preference when multiple routes exist):\n  Connected=0  Static=1  OSPF=110  RIP=120  BGP=200",
			"autoResize": true,
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"hasTextLink": false,
